    "created_at": "2015-05-12T00:26:21Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-05-12T00:27:18Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "OK I tracked it down.\nIn `Sdl2Input.cs`, where all the input handling is done, there is a `switch` with [these two cases](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/bleed/OpenRA.Renderer.Sdl2/Sdl2Input.cs#L139-L140).\nBoth of these cases trigger `inputHandler.OnKeyInput(keyEvent);`, which leads to everything being done twice on each key press.\n\nTo be honest, I'm surprised everything else that is tied to the keyboard works.\n"
  },
